<HEADLINE>
<P>
MISSOURI SYNOD DEBATES WHETHER TO CHANGE NAME 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
WICHITA, Kan. 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Delegates at the convention of the 2.6 million member Lutheran Church-Missouri 
Synod debated whether to change the name of their denomination so as better to 
reflect its national dimensions. But no action was taken about it. 
</P>
</TEXT>
