<P>
MURDOCH, RUPERT; MGM UA COMMUNICATIONS CO; QINTEX GROUP; ACQUISITIONS; 
KERKORIAN, KIRK; MOTION PICTURE INDUSTRY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
